    "description": "Kenchana : Oath of a Magical Spear is 3D beat'em up game that took place in the Old South East Archipelago Era. The era where strength of martial art determine a greatness and peace of a country but also a factor that lead to the oppressed of the weak.<br>You will be play as Kenchana one of the Royal Guard of Panji Alam Kingdom,a warrior with Light Elemental Innate that have been bestowed with a Magical Spear by the King as an exchanged to always put the kingdom security as a priority without failed.<br>A group of fierce and well known bandit called Elemental Claws has come to threaten the security of the Kingdom and it is Kenchana duty to repel the attack and take down this group of bandits.<br><br>Kenchana will fight arena by arena along the way :<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/8a4abf091e9c22b4bb0da57b17b950b6.poster.avif?t=1733787399\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/8a4abf091e9c22b4bb0da57b17b950b6.webm?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/8a4abf091e9c22b4bb0da57b17b950b6.mp4?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kenchana equipped with melee, range and dodge in his combat skills :<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/f438e1332fd37d5bfcf20182c22fa795.poster.avif?t=1733787399\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/f438e1332fd37d5bfcf20182c22fa795.webm?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/f438e1332fd37d5bfcf20182c22fa795.mp4?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kenchana will fight hordes of enemies and bosses with challenging abilities and elemental innate power. All the bosses are the master of their own element.(More will come in the final release)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/930fe2c53adc3c0638b48a4e8afe856b.poster.avif?t=1733787399\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/930fe2c53adc3c0638b48a4e8afe856b.webm?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/930fe2c53adc3c0638b48a4e8afe856b.mp4?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Skills and combos will be unlocked as the game progress to aid to face more challenging enemies:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/5b6d8c7834db6afefe0279de454bbbd9.poster.avif?t=1733787399\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/5b6d8c7834db6afefe0279de454bbbd9.webm?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250480/extras/5b6d8c7834db6afefe0279de454bbbd9.mp4?t=1733787399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
